Ndakanyatsoroorwa pa indaneti pandaive ne makore gumi namashanu.

0:01:25.740,0:01:30.720
Ichi ndicho chinhu chandisina kumbobvira ndakagovera muupenyu hwangu.

0:01:30.720,0:01:35.980
Pandakauya pano musi we Svondo, ndakanga ndakangogara kumashure uko.

0:01:35.980,0:01:41.280
Munhu wa Mwari akauya kwandiri sezvamakaona akaporofita izvo zvakanangana neni.

0:01:41.280,0:01:43.840
Ndaka katyamadzwa kwazvo nekushamisika

