uye ndakatenda Mwari kuti Akandiitira izvi

0:01:46.760,0:01:50.100
nokuti ndakanga ndisina tariro.

0:01:50.100,0:01:55.520
Apo ndakaroorwa kubva paukama hwe paindaneti ihwohwo - sezvandakuudzai ndakanga ndine makore gumi nemashanu ...

0:01:55.520,0:01:58.920
Mushure maizvozvo, muhukama hwandakanga ndawana paIndaneti ...

0:01:58.920,0:02:05.680
Pandaive ndichifambidzana ne vamwe vanhu kana ku danana ne vamwe varume, handaigutsikana.

0:02:05.680,0:02:10.380
Ndinoreva kuti chinhu chimwe chete chaigonachete kundigutsa ndechokudanana nemunhu asingazivikanwi

0:02:10.380,0:02:13.260
wandakanga ndisati ndamboona muupenyu hwangu hwose.

0:02:13.260,0:02:20.360
Saka dambudziko iri rakaita kuti ndisvute, ndaimboenda kumafaro kunonwa

0:02:20.360,0:02:23.900
pandakanga ndava nemakore gumi namashanu nehafu chete.

0:02:23.900,0:02:30.240
Zuva nezuva mumwe munhu aive pedyo neni aizoti, "Ucharega rini kusvuta?

0:02:30.240,0:02:32.260
Ucharega rini kunwa? "

0:02:32.260,0:02:39.780
Ndaiwanzonwa dhiragi rinodhaka  rinonzi ecstasy, kusvuta fodya ne 'mbanje' - 'mbanje' ndaiputa zuva rimwe nerimwe.

0:02:39.780,0:02:44.160
Gore negore, zvainyanya kuipa, kunyanya kuipa ne kuipa.

0:02:44.160,0:02:48.860
Amai vangu vakandituma pano nokuda kwenyaya iyi svondo rapera.

0:02:48.860,0:02:58.400
Pandakauya pano ndakanga ndisina tariro nokuti pose pandaienda kuchechi, kare

0:02:58.400,0:03:02.540
Ndaiwanzoudza vafundisi vaduku kuti vandidzikinure kubva mu matambudziko angu.

0:03:02.540,0:03:05.720
Zuva raitevera ndaienda kuchechi,

0:03:05.720,0:03:11.280
mufundisi aizouya kwandiri achiporofita zvose zvandakanga ndaudza vafundisi vaduku.

0:03:11.280,0:03:16.180
Ndakanga ndichiti, "Kwete." Mwari hakuna. Hachisi chokwadi, hazvikwanise kuva zvechokwadi.

0:03:16.180,0:03:20.700
