0:03:20.700,0:03:24.560
humboo hwekuti Mwari mupenyu kana kuti anoita zvishimiso huripi

0:03:24.560,0:03:28.640
Pandakauya pa SCOAN vhiki yapfuura ndokugara uko,

0:03:28.640,0:03:31.420
Ndakati ndega, "Zvakanaka, ikozvino tichaona".

0:03:31.420,0:03:34.520
Asi ndaive netariro zvechokwadi kuti hupenyu hwangu hwaizochinja.

0:03:34.520,0:03:41.340
Ndakanga ndisiri mutendi asi ini ndaizongoti, "Ndapota, Jesu, kana uri mupenyu, ndapota ndibatsirei.

0:03:41.340,0:03:44.120
Ndiri kutambura uye ndaneta nazvo ".

0:03:44.120,0:03:47.300
Nokuti hupenyu hwangu hwaivimba nezvinhu zvandaitora.

0:03:47.300,0:03:50.700
Ndairwisana nevabereki vangu; naamai vangu.

0:03:50.700,0:03:54.460
Ndakanga ndine chisimba, ndisingadzoreke.

0:03:54.460,0:03:56.760
Chisvusvuro changu chaiva fodya ne kofi.

0:03:56.760,0:03:59.640
Ndizvo zvega zvaigona kudzikamisa mweya wangu.

0:03:59.640,0:04:02.080
Kana ndisina kuwana izvozvo, kana ndisina kusvuta,

0:04:02.080,0:04:07.840
Ndaizotsamwa, kuve ne chisimba kwazvo uye ndisingaremekedze.

0:04:07.840,0:04:11.280
Kunyangwe musi we Svondo, pandakanga ndakagara uko,

0:04:11.280,0:04:14.380
mineti imwe neimwe ndaida kubuda kuti ndinosvuta.

0:04:14.380,0:04:18.320
Ndaive ndichitsvuta. Ndakasvuta midzanga mina ndisati ndauya kuchechi.

0:04:18.320,0:04:23.500
Kunyangwe pandakanga ndiri pano, ndakanga ndichirwisana nevabatsiri kuti vandibvumidze kuti ndibude kunze kuno puta.

0:04:23.500,0:04:26.840
Kuti ndakange ndizisiri kunzwa zvakanaka, ndapota.

0:04:26.840,0:04:30.520
Apo Munhu wa Mwari akauya achiporofita kwandiri,

0:04:30.520,0:04:35.640
Ini ndakati ndega, "Ndinotenda Mwari! Mune munhu wa Mwari  we chokwadi munyika ino.

0:04:35.640,0:04:38.220
Haasi munhu wose anonyengera vanhu ".

0:04:38.220,0:04:42.220
Ndakafara kwazvo; zvakaita sekuti chiroto chakave chokwadi.

0:04:42.220,0:04:47.220
Pakarepo shure kweizvozvo, vanhu va Mwari - handichaputa zvakare.

0:04:47.220,0:04:50.300
