0:04:50.300,0:04:52.060
Izvozvo hazvina kukwana kuna Jesu Kristu.

0:04:52.060,0:04:55.560
Isa maoko ako pamwe chete zvakanakisa kuna Mwari wezvichishamiso

0:04:55.560,0:04:58.240
Uchapupu Hwe Uporofita - Hwe mudzimai we chidiki Samahar Daniel

0:04:58.240,0:05:02.660
Vabereki vangu vaiwanzoenda neni kuchechi asi handina kumbobvira ndatenda mune zvose.

0:05:02.660,0:05:06.120
Asi chiitiko changu chokupedzisira chakandidzidzisa chaizvo.

0:05:06.120,0:05:10.280
Ndakazviudza kuti kana Mwari ariko zvechokwadi, Aizoita chimwe chinhu.

0:05:10.280,0:05:16.380
Ndaizotaura ndega ndichiti, "Sei musingaiti chimwe chinhu? Ndapota itai chimwe chinhu kana muri pano".

0:05:16.380,0:05:22.540
Ndakauya ku SCOAN nezvinetso zvakawanda zvinhu zvizhinji zvakaitika kwandiri.

0:05:22.540,0:05:28.080
Mai vangu avo vakandimanikidza kuti ndiuye pano - pane nguva yavange vachipikisina nazvo.

0:05:28.080,0:05:34.300
Saka izvi zvaireva chaizvo kuti zvaifanira kuitika. Mwari zvechokwadi aida kundinunura achishandisa munhu wa Mwari.

0:05:34.300,0:05:40.820
Zvakanaka, zvino iwe unogona kutiudza zvakaitika pano zvakaita kuti utende kuti Mwari ariko?

0:05:40.820,0:05:48.920
Uporofita hwaiva hwechokwadi nokuti ichi chaive chimwe chinhu chandakanga ndisina kumboudza mumwe munhu muupenyu hwangu hwose.

0:05:48.920,0:05:53.660
Izvi ndizvo zvaiva bviro bviro yematambudziko angu.

0:05:53.660,0:05:58.580
Ndicho chikonzero chakaita kuti ndive zvandaive kare.

0:05:58.580,0:06:00.660
Uye iwe hauna kumbokurukura pamusoro peizvi ne umwe munhu usati wauya pano?

0:06:00.660,0:06:03.080
Aihwa! kwete , kwete Ndakange ndisina kumboudza chero munhu.

0:06:03.080,0:06:05.840
Kunyange kwandiri - ichi ndicho chimwe chinhu chandakanga ndakanganwa.

0:06:05.840,0:06:11.740
Apo munhu wa Mwari akataura izvozvo, pakarepo ndakabva ndati, "A, Hongu! Ichokwadi!"

0:06:11.740,0:06:14.920
Apo ndakagara pachigaro, ndaive ndichifunga nezvazvo.

0:06:14.920,0:06:17.220
Husiku, ndaive ndichifunga nezvazvo.

0:06:17.220,0:06:20.200
Ndakanga ndiine ndangariro dza izvozvo.

0:06:20.200,0:06:22.220
Ndakarangarira zvose.

0:06:22.220,0:06:24.060
Zvinhu zvakatanga kuuya , kuuya.

0:06:24.060,0:06:26.140
Mwari aindiratidza, "Urikuona pandakaita izvi?"

0:06:26.140,0:06:29.480
Zvose zvakanga zvakajeka shure kweizvozvo uye zvakajeka muupenyu hwangu.

0:06:29.480,0:06:31.520
Ngatiuchirirei Jesu Kristu akanakisisa!

0:06:31.520,0:06:34.240
Uchapupu Hwe Uporofita - Hwe Mudzimai wechidiki Samahar Daniel

0:06:34.240,0:06:42.200
Zvino, mushure mokugamuchira uporofita, izvo zvakaita kuti iwe utende kuti Jesu Kristu ariko -

0:06:42.200,0:06:44.320
