0:06:44.320,0:06:48.300
Chii chaunotenda ikozvino pamusoro pehuvepo hwa Jesu?

0:06:48.300,0:06:50.960
Handina kumbobvira ndawana mufaro muhupenyu hwangu hwose.

0:06:50.960,0:06:54.460
Kwese kwandakaenda, chero chii zvacho chandakaita, ndakange ndisingafare.

0:06:54.460,0:06:57.700
Ndaiwanzoenda kumafaro, kusvuta, kuita zvinhu zvose zvakaipa.

0:06:57.700,0:07:00.080
Asi ini ndakanga ndisingambofara muupenyu hwangu hwose.

0:07:00.080,0:07:05.700
Uye hongu, ndinotenda iye zvino kuti Mwari ari pano zve chokwadi uye kuti Ano titarisa nekuti dzivirira.

0:07:05.700,0:07:10.120
Nokuti ndakapfuura mune zvakawanda, zvisinei nekuti ndaiva muduku sei.

0:07:10.120,0:07:14.500
Ndaiwanzobuda kuenda kumafaro, kunwa nekuzviona ndiine murume wandisingazive.

0:07:14.500,0:07:17.960
Saka ndaizoti , "Samahar, sei wakaita izvozvo, chii chakaitika?"

0:07:17.960,0:07:20.720
Uye izvi zvakanga zvisingatsananguriki kwandiri.

0:07:20.720,0:07:23.000
Handaikwanisa kunyange kuzvitsanangura kwandiri.

0:07:23.000,0:07:27.960
Saka hongu, Mwari akandidzivirira uye upenyu hwangu hwe kunamata kubvira ipapo hwashanduka

0:07:27.960,0:07:31.280
nokuti ndaisagara maminitsi mashanu muchechi.

0:07:31.280,0:07:34.740
Hazvina mhosva kuti amai vangu vakandiendesa kupi, vafundisi vakauya kumba kwedu vachindinamatira,

0:07:34.740,0:07:38.140
Ndaingoenda kundosvuta fodya yangu ne kukakavadzana nevanhu vose.

0:07:38.140,0:07:41.860
Kwenguva yokutanga muupenyu hwangu, ndakapinda svondo yese yakareba

0:07:41.860,0:07:43.740
kubva mangwanani kusvika usiku!

0:07:43.740,0:07:47.900
Uye ini ndinonyengetera ne kuverenga Bhaibheri.

0:07:47.900,0:07:48.980
Ndinotenda Mwari!

0:07:48.980,0:07:52.060
Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwe chete zvakanakisa kuna Mwari we zvishamiso!

0:07:52.060,0:07:55.080
Uchapupu Hwe Uporofita - Hwe Mudzimai wechidiki Samahar Daniel

0:07:55.080,0:07:59.600
Zvino kamwe zvakare, nekuda kwekunaka kweuchapupu hwako,

