0:08:04.240,0:08:07.760
Iwe ungagone zvakare here kutitaurira, pawakanga wakapinda muropa ne kuputa ikoko ne kunwa

0:08:07.760,0:08:10.940
zvaive zvakanyanya zvakadii? Zvakakanganisa hupenyu hwako hwese sei ?

0:08:10.940,0:08:13.300
Ungatiudzazve zvakare here?

0:08:13.300,0:08:21.380
Ndinofunga kuti zvichida vanhu vakambopindwa muropa kare vanozonzwisisa zvandiri kutaura chaizvo.

0:08:21.380,0:08:26.800
Nokuti kunyange kusadya kudya kwemangwanani zvakaoma kwazvo.

0:08:26.800,0:08:30.060
Pandaimuka mangwanani, chinhu chimwe chete chandaida kuita

0:08:30.060,0:08:33.320
chakanga chiri chokubatidza mudzanga nekunwa kofi.

0:08:33.320,0:08:36.820
Pane imwe nguva ndakatopisa bvudzi rangu richiedza kubatidza mudzanga we fodya.

0:08:36.820,0:08:39.880
Ndicho chinhu chega chandaida pandaimuka.

0:08:39.880,0:08:46.260
Apo vabereki vangu vakanga varipo, ndakanga ndisingagoni kusvuta ndaifanira kunyepera sekunge ndakanga ndisiri musvuti.

0:08:46.260,0:08:50.140
Zvadaro, ndaizotanga kurwa - ndaizova nehasha ne kuwana chikonzero chekubuda nekunosvuta.

0:08:50.140,0:08:53.720
Handaizombokwanisa kurega.

0:08:53.720,0:08:55.960
Ini chaizvoizvo ndaifunga kuti ndaizoguma kuputa.

0:08:55.960,0:08:57.860
Chaizvoizvo, ndaizopedzisira ndasvuta.

0:08:57.860,0:09:05.220
Munhu wose mumhuri mangu akazoziva kuti ndaimbosvuta 'mbanje' ne fodya.

0:09:05.220,0:09:10.500
Dai asiri Mwari, ndingadai ndisina kumbobvira ndabuda mumamiriro ezvinhu iwayo; ndicho chokwadi.

0:09:10.500,0:09:13.040
Uchapupu Hwe Uporofita - Hwe Mudzimai wechidiki Samahar Daniel

0:09:13.040,0:09:14.320
Kuna Mwari ngakuve ne kubwinya!

0:09:14.320,0:09:19.780
Iwe ungagone here kungotiudza kuti hukama uhwu hwawaiva nawo paIndaneti hwakakanganisa hupenyu hwako sei,

0:09:19.780,0:09:22.200
kusimbisa huporofita hwakapiwa nemunhu wa Mwari,

0:09:22.200,0:09:24.080
izvo wakati hauna kumbokurukura ne zvavo ne umwe munhu

0:09:24.080,0:09:28.820
and you were so shocked hearing that from the man of God, Prophet T.B. Joshua, for the first time last Sunday.

0:09:28.820,0:09:31.960
Ungatiudze here kuti hukama ihwohwo hwakanganisa hupenyu hwako sei semukadzi we chidiki.

0:09:31.960,0:09:36.200
Zvakandikanganisa mukuti ndakanga ndisinangambofara

0:09:36.200,0:09:40.220
Ndakanga ndisingambofara ne chero ukama hwandakanga ndinahwo.

0:09:40.220,0:09:45.440
Ndaisarudza kuva nemunhu wandakanga ndisati ndamboona - kusara kwe kuburikidza nemifananidzo chete.

0:09:45.440,0:09:49.480
Izvozvo zvaiita kuti ndigutsikane.

0:09:49.480,0:09:51.580
Izvo zvisingabatike zvaita kuti ndifare,

0:09:51.580,0:09:55.860
apo ini ndaigona kunge ndiine mumwe munhu wandaiziva nekufambidzana muupenyu pamwe chete.

0:09:55.860,0:10:00.140
Asi kwete - avo vasingazivikanwi vaiita kuti ndifare.

0:10:00.140,0:10:07.060
Zvakandikanganisa pakuti ndakanga ndisina kuvimbika kune munhu wandakanga ndiri naye.

0:10:07.060,0:10:09.080
Tinotenda Mwari Wemasimbaose nekuda kwehupenyu hwako.

0:10:09.080,0:10:14.020
