0:10:17.720,0:10:19.900
uchienzanisa noupenyu hwako hwekare?

0:10:19.900,0:10:23.880
Munoziva sezvandambokuudzai pandakasvika pano, ndakauya ndiri ndoga.

0:10:23.880,0:10:25.840
Saka ndaive ndichigara muhotera.

0:10:25.840,0:10:31.400
Mukamuri yangu yemuhotera, ndaive nemapakiti maviri emidzanga ne chekubatidzisa chimwe.

0:10:31.400,0:10:36.300
Pandakanga ndichiuya ku SCOAN kuti ndigare pano, ndakasiya zvose zvandaiva nazvo.

0:10:36.300,0:10:39.620
Uye ndakatotyamadzwa kuti a Samahar wakasiya zvose zvawaive nazvo.

0:10:39.620,0:10:41.440
Zvinoshamisa.

0:10:41.440,0:10:45.600
Ndakanga ndiri munhu aimboba chekubatidzisa fodya kubva kuvanhu. Tendai zvandiri kureva.

