Ndaitombocherechedza kana paive paketi refodya - rakakandwa pasi, ndaitarisisa kuti ndione kana paive nemidzanga mariri.

0:10:56.200,0:11:00.480
Ndingadai ndisina kumbofunga kuti ndaizosiya midzanga makumi mana shure.

0:11:00.480,0:11:02.200
Uye ini handisi kuputa.

0:11:02.200,0:11:03.920
Handichazombo svuta zvakare. Ndinotenda Mwari.

0:11:03.920,0:11:08.080
Iwe unoreva here kuti chido chekusvuta ne kunwa chapera zvachose mushure mekudzikinurwa?

0:11:08.080,0:11:09.960
Chaenda zana kubva muzana - 100%.

0:11:09.960,0:11:12.200
Ngatiuchirirei Jesu Kristu akanakisisa kune izvozvo.

0:11:12.200,0:11:15.720
Uchapupu Hwe Uporofita - Hwe Mudzimai wechidiki Samahar Daniel

0:11:15.720,0:11:18.780
Pakupedzisira, semudzimai wechidiki uyo akapfuura nemune zvakawanda pasi rose,

0:11:18.780,0:11:22.160
Jesu Kristu asati akudzikinura kubva pajoto rasatani,

0:11:22.160,0:11:25.580
nderipi shoko rezano raunaro kune vanhu pasi rose,

0:11:25.580,0:11:28.560
kunyanya kune vechidiki vatori muhusungwa hwakadaro?

0:11:28.560,0:11:30.380
Iwe unovayambira kuti kudii?

